title: 2 bedroom 1st floor
posting_body: Nice first floor 2 bedroom apartment with plenty of closet space, just painted and put new floors.
Heat is included in the rent.
Free laundry in the basement, free internet.
To save your valuable time and mine, I ask for this basic info before making an appointment as an effort to reduce unnecessary calls and trips for both you and me.
